# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:67
msgid ""
"Interpolated values use a quadratic curve, and ease-in and ease-out. Icon: "
":guilabel:`Circle`."
msgstr "插值數值使用二次曲線，並具有緩入緩出效果。圖示：:guilabel:`圓形` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid "Linear"
msgstr "線性"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid ""
"Interpolated values are calculated linear (each step value is equal). Icon: "
":guilabel:`Diamond`."
msgstr "插值數值以線性計算（每步數值相等）。圖示：:guilabel:`菱形` 。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid "Constant"
msgstr "常數"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Interpolated values stay the same until the next key frame, and jump to the "
"new value. Icon: :guilabel:`Square`."
msgstr "插值數值保持不變直到下一個關鍵影格，然後跳至新數值。圖示：:guilabel:`方形` 。"

