msgid "Frame Rate"
msgstr "影格率"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:134
msgid ""
"Adjust the frame rate of the animation. Typically, hand-drawn animations use"
" 12 frames per second."
msgstr "調整動畫的影格率。通常手繪動畫使用每秒 12 影格。"
